<l>niṉaippavar pōṉṟu niṉaiyārkol tummal </l>
<l> ciṉaippatu pōṉṟu keṭum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I feel as if I am going to sneeze but do not, and (therefore) my beloved is about to think (of me) but does not.</l>
